{"tid":643894,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"郭可盈送二手野比佢兩個姪女","createTime":"2018-04-26T23:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T06:52:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0218f5b374b0b0faad823de9764a5679446c0455","tid":643894,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T23:24:46.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】37歲熊黛林（Lynn）日前為老公郭可頌誕下孖女，郭可頌今午4時許獨自駕車返家，泊車後走到屋苑另一端上樓。<br />\n<br />\n約1分鐘後，其姊郭可盈離開屋苑，向記者透露BB在睡覺，「好可愛，一個似爸爸，一個似媽媽。<span style=\"color: red;\">可盈又表示送了珍貴禮物給BB，是「LUCK」，原來是她囡囡穿過的衫</span>，寓意孖女快高長大。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/G04rDdQgdEqPNw6zDxmzLg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180426f183850.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FG04rDdQgdEqPNw6zDxmzLg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180426f183850.jpg&h=df94cfe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n郭可盈咁有錢,送份禮物都咁寒酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45b480274aef6c7aaffd5b05282798a8e477333","tid":643894,"uid":40470,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T23:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連登弱智仔咁都有得反<br />\n<br />\n送舊衫比初出生bb確實係意頭野<br />\n<br />\n想知樓主條柒頭搵錢有無郭既十份之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8bbcd63c339e8a1610bea36f4cda9fcb9ea66cc","tid":643894,"uid":33497,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T23:55:13.000Z","msg":"瘦到好撚核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab7ae39411c76f1f1b69edc372fa7f0b4cea7094","tid":643894,"uid":81569,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T23:57:01.000Z","msg":"當年一代美人<i